		
		<a href='./'><img class='logo' src='graphics/logo.png' width='506' height='32' border='0' alt='Link to uberChicGeekChick.Com: home of *unallocated_pointer( the open source art podcast );' title='*unallocated_pointer( the open source art podcast );' /></a>
		<img class='slogan' src='graphics/slogan.png' width='373' height='26' alt='podcast *unallocated_pointed = the art of open source & art created using open source software' title='podcast *unallocated_pointed = the art of open source & art created using open source software'>
		
